      <body>
         <p>Use the General Multiplication Rule to find the probability that the engine is overheating and a warning shows up.</p>
      </body>
      <short_answer id="A"/>
      <part>
         <response input="A" match="*" score="1"/>
         <explanation>
            <p>We need to find: P(H and W). Using the General Multiplication Rule:</p>
            <p>P(H and W) = P(H) * P(W | H) = .03 * .98 = .0294.</p>
         </explanation>
